README

 4DTRIS
 Created by Simon, Laszlo

 This Application is a Tetris game extended to 4 dimension. The
 visulaization uses OpenGL and GLUT.

 Project web page: dtris.sourceforge.net

 ---

 Install:
 $ cd src
 $ make all
 $ ./4dtris

 Dependency:
 - OpenGL
 - GLU
 - GLUT
 ---

 Game Controls:
 - esc              - menu
 - arrow keys       - rotate the view port
 - z, x, c, v       - turn the blocks around the 4 axis
 - 1, 2, 3          - select rotation axles
 - a                - auto player on/off
 - +, -, pgdn, pgup - rotate around selected axle
 - home, end        - rot. around selected and 4th axle

